title: Manzariyeh Rural District
text: Manzariyeh Rural District () is a <a href="Rural%20Districts%20of%20Iran">rural district</a> ("dehestan") in the <a href="Central%20District%20%28Shahreza%20County%29">Central District</a> of <a href="Shahreza%20County">Shahreza County</a>, <a href="Isfahan%20Province">Isfahan Province</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>. At the 2006 census, its population was 11,643, in 2,995 families. The rural district has 26 villages.
